author: Graphic Designer 2
title: Jennings’ Etienne selected as Gatorade POY finalist
text: Jennings’ Etienne selected as Gatorade POY finalist By DYLAN BROSSETTE Daily News Sports Editor In light of the on-going superlative junior season for Jennings running back Travis Etienne Jr., the sports drink Gatorade, in conjunction with USA Today , announced this Tuesday Etienne was one of 12 finalists for the brand’s coveted “Gatorade Player of the Year” award for prep football in the state of Louisiana.  //www.jenningsdailynews.net/?p=34410   23
